name: Over-Fed
description:
A game about making good food choices.

You play as a person who is trying to go on a diet, however temptation in the form of junk food literally comes from all sides

Your Objective:

attempt to kill temptation by avoiding junk food

get healthy power-ups along the way to help you in your journey.

Power-ups include:

Speedy Beans - beans to increase speed (what were u expecting?)

Healthy Milk - milk that decreases your chonk 

Super Smoothie - unleash a barrage of knives to destroy nearby junk food
